Congrès Mondial des Études sur le Moyen-Orient. 16 au 20 juillet 2018

   Seville, 16-20 July 2018 – The World Congress for Middle Eastern
   Studies (WOCMES) is a gathering of scholars, researchers, students and
   professionals drawn from a broad range of educational and other
   institutions, organizations and associations from around the world.

